  "title": "Use Glowstone Dust as Glow Ink Sacs",
  "description": "Craft Glow Item Frame and make Signs glow by using Glowstone Dust",
  "body": "<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> <a href=\"https://discord.gg/2CUh6gMuCt\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1027252425960198165?color=5b6ee1&amp;label=Discord&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"Discord\" /></a> <a href=\"https://patreon.com/MarsThePlanet\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint.svg?url=https%3A%2F%2Fshieldsio-patreon.vercel.app%2Fapi%3Fusername%3DMarsThePlanet%26type%3Dpatrons&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"Support me on Patreon\" /></a> <a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/server/phobos/\"><img title=\"phobos.mcserv.fun\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint?url=https%3A%2F%2Fminecraft-server-status-badge.vercel.app%2Fapi%2Fserver%2Fphobos.mcserv.fun%3Fport%3D25565&amp;label=anarchy server&amp;style=for-the-badge\" /></a> </strong></h5>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">With this Fabric mod, you no longer need to use Glow Ink Sacs to glow up your world. I made this mod because I feel like the Glow Ink Sacs were added only due to the mob vote even tho they have no utility that couldn't be done by Glowstone dust.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8nZZ2DN.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"568\" height=\"225\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/oxj7NH7.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"490\" height=\"268\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/use-glowstone-dust-as-glow-ink-sac\"> This mod on CurseForge</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/marstheplanet\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FQLov3P.png\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://patreon.com/MarsThePlanet\"><img src=\"https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/5968/5968732.png\" alt=\"Support me on Patreon\" width=\"30\" /></a> Patrons:</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/zoopla2323\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span class=\"sc-ieecCq gLfHQe\" data-tag=\"user-details-full-name\">Linkyboy Hendrie</span></a></li>\n</ul>",
